  "ps3.8:7.25": "“vedanāsu vedanānupassanāsatipaṭṭhānā”. ",
  "ps3.8:8.1": "**Bhāvanā**ti catasso bhāvanā …pe… ",
  "ps3.8:8.2": "evaṁ vedanāsu vedanānupassī viharati. ",
  "ps3.8:9.1": "Kathaṁ **citte cittānupassī viharati?** ",
  "ps3.8:9.2": "Idhekacco sarāgaṁ cittaṁ aniccato anupassati, no niccato …pe… ",
