  "ps3.8:9.4": "Aniccato anupassanto niccasaññaṁ pajahati …pe… ",
  "ps3.8:9.5": "paṭinissajjanto ādānaṁ pajahati. ",
  "ps3.8:9.6": "Imehi sattahi ākārehi cittaṁ anupassati. ",
  "ps3.8:9.7": "Cittaṁ upaṭṭhānaṁ, no sati. ",
  "ps3.8:9.8": "Sati upaṭṭhānañceva sati ca. ",
  "ps3.8:9.9": "Tāya satiyā tena ñāṇena taṁ cittaṁ anupassati. ",
  "ps3.8:9.10": "Tena vuccati—",
  "ps3.8:9.11": "“citte cittānupassanāsatipaṭṭhānā”. ",
