  "ps3.8:13.1": "Kathaṁ **dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati?** ",
  "ps3.8:13.2": "Idhekacco ṭhapetvā kāyaṁ ṭhapetvā vedanaṁ ṭhapetvā cittaṁ tadavasese dhamme aniccato anupassati, no niccato; ",
  "ps3.8:13.3": "dukkhato anupassati, no sukhato; ",
  "ps3.8:13.4": "anattato anupassati, no attato; ",
  "ps3.8:13.5": "nibbindati, no nandati; ",
  "ps3.8:13.6": "virajjati, no rajjati; ",
  "ps3.8:13.7": "nirodheti, no samudeti; ",
  "ps3.8:13.8": "paṭinissajjati, no ādiyati. ",
  "ps3.8:13.9": "Aniccato anupassanto niccasaññaṁ pajahati, dukkhato anupassanto sukhasaññaṁ pajahati, anattato anupassanto attasaññaṁ pajahati, nibbindanto nandiṁ pajahati, virajjanto rāgaṁ pajahati, nirodhento samudayaṁ pajahati, paṭinissajjanto ādānaṁ pajahati. ",
  "ps3.8:13.10": "Imehi sattahi ākārehi te dhamme anupassati. ",
  "ps3.8:13.11": "Dhammā upaṭṭhānaṁ, no sati. ",
  "ps3.8:13.12": "Sati upaṭṭhānañceva sati ca. ",
  "ps3.8:13.13": "Tāya satiyā tena ñāṇena te dhamme anupassati. ",
  "ps3.8:13.14": "Tena vuccati—",
  "ps3.8:13.15": "“dhammesu dhammānupassanāsatipaṭṭhānā”. ",
  "ps3.8:14.1": "**Bhāvanā**ti catasso bhāvanā—",
  "ps3.8:14.2": "tattha jātānaṁ dhammānaṁ anativattanaṭṭhena bhāvanā, indriyānaṁ ekarasaṭṭhena bhāvanā, tadupagavīriyavāhanaṭṭhena bhāvanā, āsevanaṭṭhena bhāvanā. ",
  "ps3.8:14.3": "Evaṁ dhammesu dhammānupassī viharatīti. ",
  "ps3.8:14.4": "Satipaṭṭhānakathā niṭṭhitā. "
